      プログラマー
    </p>

    <div class="flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap mb-8">
      <a
        href="/works"
        class="px-8 py-3 bg-purple-500 dark:bg-purple-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-purple-700 dark:hover:bg-purple-800 transition-colors duration-200"
      >
        My Works
      </a>
      <a
        href="/about"
